      <title>捷克武器生产商 CSG 报告去年销售额创纪录 1.7 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/czech-arms-producer-csg-reports-record-1-7b-sales-for-last-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[武器生产商捷克斯洛伐克集团去年公布了创纪录的销售额和盈利能力，因为乌克兰战争增加了对这家总部位于布拉格的公司生产的重型弹药和战车的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/czech-arms-producer-csg-reports-record-1-7b-sales-for-last-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯表示，他对杜特尔特与中国的海上协议感到“震惊”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/marcos-says-he-s-horrified-of-duterte-sea-deal-with-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯表示，他“震惊”地得知他的前任罗德里戈·杜特尔特与中国之间达成了一项协议，禁止马尼拉向南海争议浅滩的军事前哨运送建筑材料。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/marcos-says-he-s-horrified-of-duterte-sea-deal-with-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 06:48:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国将通过预算提供 140 亿美元现金补助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/thailand-to-fund-14-billion-cash-handout-through-state-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国将为一项 140 亿美元的现金发放计划提供资金，通过国家预算和国家银行的援助相结合来刺激经济，搁置先前诉诸一次性借款的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/thailand-to-fund-14-billion-cash-handout-through-state-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 04:56:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>立陶宛称“没有时间”来对抗俄罗斯的战时经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/-no-time-to-lose-against-russia-s-war-economy-lithuania-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[立陶宛国防部长表示，随着欧洲军事工业提高产量以跟上俄罗斯战时经济的步伐，北约“刻不容缓”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/-no-time-to-lose-against-russia-s-war-economy-lithuania-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称他可能有权自行关闭边境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/biden-says-he-may-have-authority-to-close-border-on-his-own</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，他仍在考虑采取单方面行动关闭美国南部边境，并研究他是否有法律权力在未经国会批准的情况下这样做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/biden-says-he-may-have-authority-to-close-border-on-his-own</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 03:45:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>即将上任的台湾领导人专注于总理选择的连续性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/incoming-taiwan-leader-focuses-on-continuity-with-premier-pick</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将上任的台湾总统赖清德选择了一位曾在现任政府任职的资深官员担任总理，这凸显了他对连续性的推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/incoming-taiwan-leader-focuses-on-continuity-with-premier-pick</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 03:15:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港大楼火灾造成至少4人死亡、12人受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-10/urgent-hong-kong-building-fire-kills-at-least-4-people-and-injures-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港（美联社）——周三上午，香港一栋主要为住宅的大型建筑发生火灾，造成至少 5 人死亡，另有 34 人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-10/urgent-hong-kong-building-fire-kills-at-least-4-people-and-injures-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 02:57:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国检察官推迟对他信皇室侮辱案下达命令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/thai-prosecutors-delay-decision-on-thaksin-s-royal-insult-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国检察官推迟了是否在皇家侮辱案中起诉前总理他信的决定，原因是他信在近十年前发表的言论可能会让这位有影响力的政治家在去年结束 15 年流亡后回国后陷入新的法律麻烦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/thai-prosecutors-delay-decision-on-thaksin-s-royal-insult-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 02:36:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉姆·伊曼纽尔表示，美国寻求在盟友的帮助下孤立中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/us-seeks-to-isolate-china-with-help-of-allies-ambassador-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻日本大使拉姆·伊曼纽尔表示，乔·拜登总统的政府正在寻求在日本和该地区其他盟友的帮助下扭转中国孤立包括菲律宾在内的亚洲国家的企图。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/us-seeks-to-isolate-china-with-help-of-allies-ambassador-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 01:14:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国在总统公投中投票支持议会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/south-korea-votes-for-new-parliament-in-referendum-on-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国民众在尹锡烈总统任期内举行的唯一一次全民公投中选举新议会，这将决定他在剩余三年任期内将拥有多少权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/south-korea-votes-for-new-parliament-in-referendum-on-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 21:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
